'''Flatbeds''' were military gunships used by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] near the end of the [[New Sith Wars]]. They were armored [[Repulsorcraft/Legends|repulsorcraft]] with a flatbed rear. The rear had a wall high enough to protect the occupants, who could duck behind them when reloading.

During the [[Battle of Phaseera]], the [[Gloom Walkers]] attacked a Republic fortification equipped with three flatbeds.

==Behind the scenes==
Flatbeds appeared in the novel [[Darth Bane: Path of Destruction]], written by [[Drew Karpyshyn]] and released on [[September 26]], [[2006]].

